103
00:06:49,540 --> 00:06:51,584
Given those possible solutions,

104
00:06:51,584 --> 00:06:56,520
the next step is to analyze systematically the solutions against the criteria that

105
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:59,423
you established for what a solution ought have.

