00:06:59,423 --> 00:07:04,214
And select the ones that are the most promising, that can be elaborated and

107
00:07:04,214 --> 00:07:06,610
brought forward to the next phases.

108
00:07:06,610 --> 00:07:10,180
The next step is to embody those solution which means to build

109
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:14,020
some kind of a prototype that can be used for

110
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:16,930
